{"tid":2238205,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿富汗激進組織「神學士」支持川普連任 競選團隊婉拒","createTime":"2020-10-11T03:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T03:14:26.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d846e0a071c21b298d744582d86de1f01415a3e6","tid":2238205,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕阿富汗伊斯蘭教激進組織「神學士」（Taliban）表態支持美國總統川普，希望他勝選並從阿富汗撤軍，還關心川普感染武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）後的健康狀況，不過川普團隊婉拒「神學士」的力挺。<br />\n<br />\n「神學士」發言人穆賈希德（Zabihullah Mujahid）接受美國媒體《CBS新聞》（CBS News）採訪，在採訪中大讚美國總統川普對「神學士」的態度相當理性明智，他表態：「我們希望他能贏得選舉，結束美國在阿富汗的軍事存在」<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n不過川普競選團隊公關主任墨托（Tim Murtaugh）透過聲明指出，「我們拒絕神學士的支持」，他指出神學士應該知道總統本人始終以一切必要手段保護美國利益，這與拜登不同。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3317810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3317810&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlRVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=c423acd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3317810&h=08ecf7ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3317810</a>"},{"pid":"d6c1c90949d1567c26d34b54cc694bd1bf370de0","tid":2238205,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"連 Taliban 都撐侵侵，希望美國人會覺醒投番侵侵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}